   FEE SCHEDULES

   The Board is a special fund agency which derives its operating monies
   from its licensees and examination applicants. The Board's sole source
   of revenue is based upon the fees charged.

   VOCATIONAL NURSE FEES

   *This fee does not include the NCLEX Registration Fee, which eligible
   applicants must submit to the NCLEX Data Center to register for the
   vocational nursing examination.

   Revenue Category

                                    Fee Amount Effective 1/1/2000

   Initial Application

                                                                    $75.00*

   Reexamination Application

                                                                    $75.00*

   Interim Permit

                                                                    $40.00

   Initial License for 2 years

                                                                    $100.00

   Renewal Fee for 2 years

                                                                    $100.00

   Delinquent Fee

                                                                    $50.00

   Duplicate License

                                                                    $25.00

   Endorsements

                                                                    $75.00

   Continuing Education Provider Fee

                                                                    $200.00
